# Cursor Rules

## Commit Message Conventions

> **Single Source of Truth:** The commit message conventions are defined in `.cursor/commands/generate-commit-message.md`. Always reference and follow the rules from that file when generating commit messages.

When generating commit messages (via "Generate Commit Message" button in source control or when asked to write commit messages), always reference and follow the commit message conventions defined in `.cursor/commands/generate-commit-message.md`.
